Trade/Device Name(s): Dochek® Fentanyl Urine Test Strip Plus
Dochek® Fentanyl Urine Test Card Plus
Dochek® Fentanyl Urine Test Cup Plus
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Dochek Fentanyl Urine Test system for qualitative detection of fentanyl in urine by lateral flow immunoassay
Indications for Use Summary: Qualitative detection of fentanyl (FTY) in human urine at 1 ng/mL cutoff using lateral flow immunochromatographic assay; provides preliminary results, requires confirmatory testing with GC/MS or LC/MS, for OTC and professional use
